      "blocks": {
        "text_UFyhpT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Philantropica may look like pure indulgence. Beneath the surface sits something else entirely. Every Philantropica purchase helps fund the removal of ocean-bound plastic before it reaches the sea.</p><p>Philantropica is 100% not-for-profit and all proceeds go to the Philantropica Fund, supporting plastic collection projects and ocean health initiatives.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_mBFJw4": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p>There are no beaches on Mars.</p>",
            "heading_size": "fh4"
          }
        },
        "text_9ntT4M": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The ocean covers 70% of the planet, produces half the oxygen we breathe, feeds 3 billion people, and is the world’s largest carbon sink. What happens beneath the surface affects everyone above it. </p><p>With this impending doom, some people are making plans to go live on a rock in space with temperatures of -100°C. But we say: no beach, no fun.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
